
Overview of noun reincarnation

The noun reincarnation has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                
1. reincarnation -- (embodiment in a new form (especially the reappearance or a person in another form); "his reincarnation as a lion")
2. reincarnation, rebirth, renascence -- (a second or new birth)
3. reincarnation -- (the Hindu or Buddhist doctrine that a person may be reborn successively into one of five classes of living beings (god or human or animal or hungry ghost or denizen of Hell) depending on the person's own actions)
